            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://www.modernhealthcare.com/government/insurer-hospital-lobbyists-unite-against-medicare-all-proposals",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " about helping create a major health care industry dark money group working to convince Americans that the corporate insurance system is great, and that popular programs like Medicare should not be expanded.",
