          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " thanked the Biden administration for moving to stop these retroactive ER denials, and adds more detail about the various ways insurers are selecting claims to deny.",
            "type": "text",
