            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Corporate insurers might put patients through hell and make hospital staff jump through insane bureaucratic hoops, but insurers pay hospitals far more for services than the government ever would. On average, hospitals bill people with private health insurance plans ",
