          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "That’s why hospital executives will do anything to make sure nothing about our health care system ever fundamentally changes. And it’s why hospitals are pouring money into campaigns to protect health insurers’ market share, and telling the public everything is fine — even though insurers have every incentive to deny claims and try to pass costs on to patients or providers.",
